description: If you could have loved this one, it may have been special. There was always something distant and unreachable, even when you were fucking her - You wanted to finish, but it was too much of a turn off, someone disengaged like that. You got her off with your hands, and smoked a spliff out on the balcony while she wept. Someone else would have to ignight that hearth.
name: Violet Weng
